            <h4 class="mt-3" style="color: #7588fd">Inclusive Educational Game Development Competition for Persons with Intellectual
                Disabilities</h5>
                <p class="mt-3 fw-semibold">
                    Are you passionate about transforming the education landscape with cutting-edge technology? Here's
                    your chance to shine! We invite innovators, tech enthusiasts, and visionary minds to participate in
                    the pioneering AR/VR eLearning Hackathon 2024. This is not just a hackathon; it's a movement to
                    revolutionise learning experiences!
                </p>
                <div class="card mb-3">

                    <div class="card-body d-block fw-semibold">

                        <h5 style="color: #7588fd">Why Participate?</h5>

                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                Collaborate with Brilliance: Join a community of talented developers, creative
                                designers, and educational experts driving the next wave of digital learning.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Showcase Your Talent: Whether you're a seasoned developer or a budding innovator, this
                                is your platform to shine and showcase your skills to industry leaders.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Win Exciting Prizes and Recognition: Attractive rewards await the most innovative
                                solutions that can redefine eLearning through immersive AR and VR technologies. The
                                winners will also be honoured with certificates from the Ministry of Electronics and
                                Information Technology (Meity), adding a prestigious accolade to their professional
                                portfolio.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Network with Industry Stalwarts: Engage with tech gurus, business leaders, and
                                eLearning experts. Expand your professional network and open doors to new opportunities.
                            </li>
                        </ul>

