                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                Idea-Thon: A dedicated segment to brainstorm and pitch groundbreaking ideas that blend
                                AR/VR with eLearning. It's not just about ideas; it's about redefining the way we learn
                                and teach.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Build & Test: Develop prototypes with state-of-the-art tools and receive real-time
                                feedback from AR/VR users and eLearning experts.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Masterclass Sessions: Learn from the best in the industry. Exclusive workshops on the
                                latest AR/VR tools, design thinking, and eLearning trends.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Final Showdown: Present your solution to a panel of esteemed judges and stand a chance
                                to win and get your project incubated.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
