                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                The winner will be decided based on the best idea to create high-quality 2D, 3D, and
                                AR/VR content as quickly as possible. We are looking for solutions that excel in
                                innovation, usability, and impact, regardless of the tools or technology involved. Show
                                us how your idea can transform eLearning with speed and quality!
                            </li>
                        </ul>
